        <item>
			<title>Episode #10: Some Bully Bosses Forbid Bathroom Breaks?!</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UndercoverLawyerPodcast/~3/8LnopBmNkMY/episode-10-some-bully-bosses-forbid-bathroom-breaks-</link>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Main Segment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the Main Segment of Episode #10 we tackle the issue of &amp;quot;Bully Bosses Who Forbid Bathroom Breaks.&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp; This craziness happens much more frequently than you may think.&amp;nbsp; Can you guess who the primary victims are?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;"&gt;#1 Spanish radio station in Miami
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The radio show I mention during the show is 98.3.&amp;nbsp; My thanks to Frank, the Undercover Lawyer community member from Miami
who got the book and called in to 98.3 to talk about it.&amp;nbsp; Thanks Frank!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;








